@author Yassine El Khadiri

Modules contained in this project :

* Generator: Generates traffic on the bus to test the other modules.
	    In this project it copies data from memory to memory
    Files:
	Generator.h
	Generator.cpp

* Bus: Handles communication between modules
    Files:
	bus.h
	bus.cpp

* LCDC: display module that shows the content of a given address range
    Files:
	LCDC.h
	LCDC.cpp
	LCDC_registermap.h (unused, see defines.h)

* memory: storage module for the embedded software and video memory
    Files:
	memory.h
	memory.cpp

* ROM: storage module containing a picture
    Files:
	ROM.h
	ROM.cpp
	ROM_content.h

* sc_main.cpp: This is where the modules are put and connected together

* defines.h: This is where system-wide configuration is set.
		(address ranges, memory sizes and miscellaneous convenient
		    defines...)
